name: Astaroth
description:
The archduke of the underworld and the one in charge of guarding the riches of this place, no mortal or demon can reach these riches.

The reason why no one can reach the treasures without him realizing it is because in his eyes he has the power to see the past, the present and the future that lies ahead. With an infinite capacity to detect the deepest desires of those who approach him, which makes him impossible to deceive.
